<subSubSection pageId="27" pageNumber="28" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="27.[264,1323,356,862]" box="[264,383,356,381]" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">
<emphasis box="[264,383,356,381]" italics="true" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">Diagnosis</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="27.[264,1323,356,862]" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">
Dark brown to black, base of elytron with brick red marks. Pronotum transverse with lateral margin strongly convex (
<figureCitation box="[642,738,436,462]" captionStart="FIGURE 7. A. A" captionStartId="14.[264,367,1433,1457]" captionTargetBox="[313,1269,477,1408]" captionTargetId="figure@14.[302,1293,466,1408]" captionTargetPageId="14" captionText="FIGURE 7. A. A. sordidus, pronotum (dorsal view); B. A. guttatus, prosternum (lateral view); C. A. guttatus, prosternum (ventral view); D. A. atratus, left elytron, dashed line indicates explanate margin; E. A. sordidus, left elytron, dashed line indicates explanate margin; F. A. sordidus, anal sclerite (ventral view); G. A. kauaiensis, apex of anal sclerite; H. Orthostolus nsp., metafemur (ventral view); I. A. guttatus, metafemur (ventral view); J. A. guttatus, labial palp (ventral view); K. Eupetinus impressus, labial palp (ventral view); L A. atratus, anal sclerite (ventral view)." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/175095/files/figure.png" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">
Fig. 
<number box="[698,713,436,462]" pageId="27" pageNumber="28" value="7.0">7</number>
A
</figureCitation>
). Elytron with lateral margin narrow, 
<date box="[1185,1214,436,462]" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">
<number box="[1185,1199,436,462]" pageId="27" pageNumber="28" value="2.0">2</number>
x
</date>
width of bead at middle, sometimes wider at humeri (
<figureCitation box="[780,849,476,502]" captionStart="FIGURE 7. A. A" captionStartId="14.[264,367,1433,1457]" captionTargetBox="[313,1269,477,1408]" captionTargetId="figure@14.[302,1293,466,1408]" captionTargetPageId="14" captionText="FIGURE 7. A. A. sordidus, pronotum (dorsal view); B. A. guttatus, prosternum (lateral view); C. A. guttatus, prosternum (ventral view); D. A. atratus, left elytron, dashed line indicates explanate margin; E. A. sordidus, left elytron, dashed line indicates explanate margin; F. A. sordidus, anal sclerite (ventral view); G. A. kauaiensis, apex of anal sclerite; H. Orthostolus nsp., metafemur (ventral view); I. A. guttatus, metafemur (ventral view); J. A. guttatus, labial palp (ventral view); K. Eupetinus impressus, labial palp (ventral view); L A. atratus, anal sclerite (ventral view)." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/175095/files/figure.png" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">
Fig. 
<number box="[834,849,476,502]" pageId="27" pageNumber="28" value="7.0">7</number>
</figureCitation>
D). Pale marks on elytra most prominent along base, often continuing along suture to apical margin. Male pygidium narrow, subtruncate to shallowly emarginate, anal sclerite with lateral apical margin concave and convergent, apex acuminate (
<figureCitation box="[622,696,596,622]" captionStart="FIGURE 7. A. A" captionStartId="14.[264,367,1433,1457]" captionTargetBox="[313,1269,477,1408]" captionTargetId="figure@14.[302,1293,466,1408]" captionTargetPageId="14" captionText="FIGURE 7. A. A. sordidus, pronotum (dorsal view); B. A. guttatus, prosternum (lateral view); C. A. guttatus, prosternum (ventral view); D. A. atratus, left elytron, dashed line indicates explanate margin; E. A. sordidus, left elytron, dashed line indicates explanate margin; F. A. sordidus, anal sclerite (ventral view); G. A. kauaiensis, apex of anal sclerite; H. Orthostolus nsp., metafemur (ventral view); I. A. guttatus, metafemur (ventral view); J. A. guttatus, labial palp (ventral view); K. Eupetinus impressus, labial palp (ventral view); L A. atratus, anal sclerite (ventral view)." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/175095/files/figure.png" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">
Fig. 
<number box="[681,696,596,622]" pageId="27" pageNumber="28" value="7.0">7</number>
</figureCitation>
F), broader at base than apex of pygidium. Length 
<quantity box="[264,401,636,662]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.05" metricValueMax="5.5" metricValueMin="4.6" pageId="27" pageNumber="28" unit="mm" value="5.05" valueMax="5.5" valueMin="4.6">4.6–5.5mm</quantity>
, Width 
<quantity box="[492,629,636,662]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.0999999999999996" metricValueMax="2.3" metricValueMin="1.9" pageId="27" pageNumber="28" unit="mm" value="2.0999999999999996" valueMax="2.3" valueMin="1.9">1.9–2.3mm</quantity>
.
</paragraph>
